# iOS Calculator

This is a simple calculator made for iOS devices that is meant to properly calculate the values provided using basic operations including multiplication, dividion, addition, and subtraction.

## How to run
Open the project using Xcode by opening the Calculator.xcodeproj file. Once the project is up on Xcode you can hit the Run button to run the project in the provided iOS simulator.

## Notes
-Once value is calculated it may show trailing zeros
-If value is divided by zero, the calculator will default the answer to be infiniti for that particular calculation. If there are other operations in the equation it will only treat that specific calculation as zero, not the entire equation.